    Report Reusable Functions which can be called at any point of time while automating your application.

    Author: VuramAutomationTeam

    • Startreport

      public void Startreport(java.lang.String TestcaseDescription,
                        java.lang.String TCID,
                        java.lang.String suitename)
                 throws java.lang.Exception
      Method used to create an extent report
      Parameters:
      TestcaseDescription - Description about the test case
      TCID - Drop Test case ID of the test case
      suitename - Regression suite name for which the user going to run this automation suite`(For Example: public void Startreport("Regression Flow","TC001","Regression Suite"))
      Throws:
      java.lang.Exception - This exception will be thrown, if an error occurs while creating an extent report

    • StepPassWithoutScreenshot

      public void StepPassWithoutScreenshot(java.lang.String passstep)
                               throws java.io.IOException
      Method used to log a test step as pass
      Parameters:
      passstep - Pass step details which needs to be displayed in the extent report - (For Example: public void StepPass("Log in to an application"))
      Throws:
      java.io.IOException - This exception will be thrown, if an error occurs while logging a pass step details in extent report

    • ResultValidation

      public void ResultValidation(java.lang.String TCID,
                             java.lang.String ExcelFilepath,
                             java.lang.String Excelsheetpath,
                             java.lang.String Columnnames)
                      throws java.lang.Exception
      Method used to check the result of the test case from the extent report and copy it in Result log excel sheet
      Parameters:
      TCID - TCID in the input data sheet for which the user needs to check the result
      ExcelFilepath - File path of the result log sheet
      Excelsheetpath - Sheet name of the result log sheet
      Columnnames - Column name where the user needs to store the result - (For Example: public String ResultValidation("TC001","C://Resultlog.xlsx","Resultlog","Result"))
      Throws:
      java.lang.Exception - This exception will be thrown, if an error occurs while checking the test case result from the extent report
